# Electron & Terminal Rules

## Process split
- **POS/KDS renderer**: UI only, IPC to local-agent
- **local-agent**: SQLite, sync, printers, WebSocket, watchdog

## POS Electron
- `--kiosk` fullscreen, single BrowserWindow
- `ELECTRON_DISABLE_DEV_TOOLS=true` in production
- No Node integration in renderer; use preload + contextBridge
- Auto-update via electron-updater on shift close

## local-agent
- HTTP on `127.0.0.1:3456` for POS IPC
- SQLite WAL mode at `/data/local.db`
- Sync poll: 5s interval, batch 50, FIFO queue
- Watchdog: check every 5s, max 3 restarts per 10 min

## Printers
- ESC/POS via agent, UTF-8 encoding
- 3 retries then alert; fallback to KDS if kitchen printer down

## Lightweight
- No moment.js, no full lodash, no heavy icon packs in POS
- Lazy-load menu images from server
- Combined RAM target: < 300 MB
